      <p>My guys all trust me to keep their accounts balanced so they can keep freight moving and checks rolling in.</p>
      <p>I use my knowledge to Edjimacate drivers on how to win during tax season and win in personal finance.</p>
      <p>If you love the freedom of the open road as much as you love earning money, you need someone like me--
      I can show you how to stay financially free and to keep your dollars in your pocket.</p>
      <p><a class="btn btn-kor" href="#reg">That's what I need!</a></p>
      <p><a class=" btn btn-kor" href="#feature1">Edjimacate me.</a></p>
    </div>
